  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minimalist Survival</h2><strong>INEVITABLE LIGHT</strong> is a minimalist Open World Survival game set in a brutal desert environment.  <br><strong>On this permanent death journey, your decisions are your greatest enemy</strong>. <br><br>Explore the sandy dunes and its mysteries as you hunt for food, water, and shelter. Constantly threatened by the desert, you’ll fight through sand storms, starvation, dehydration, boiling and freezing temperatures as you cling to life. <strong>Survive for as long as you can</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/1ffa0f8d5d559451ba2bd10c0a11d6bf.poster.avif?t=1756124621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/1ffa0f8d5d559451ba2bd10c0a11d6bf.webm?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/1ffa0f8d5d559451ba2bd10c0a11d6bf.mp4?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight the extreme temperatures of the desert by sheltering-in on hot days, navigating through dune shades or cooler evenings, and firing things up on freezing nights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/5584b3ed5f6dfb4ad28b012b781ad044.poster.avif?t=1756124621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/5584b3ed5f6dfb4ad28b012b781ad044.webm?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/5584b3ed5f6dfb4ad28b012b781ad044.mp4?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minimalist Survival</h2><strong>INEVITABLE LIGHT</strong> is a minimalist Open World Survival game set in a brutal desert environment.  <br><strong>On this permanent death journey, your decisions are your greatest enemy</strong>. <br><br>Explore the sandy dunes and its mysteries as you hunt for food, water, and shelter. Constantly threatened by the desert, you’ll fight through sand storms, starvation, dehydration, boiling and freezing temperatures as you cling to life. <strong>Survive for as long as you can</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/1ffa0f8d5d559451ba2bd10c0a11d6bf.poster.avif?t=1756124621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/1ffa0f8d5d559451ba2bd10c0a11d6bf.webm?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/1ffa0f8d5d559451ba2bd10c0a11d6bf.mp4?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight the extreme temperatures of the desert by sheltering-in on hot days, navigating through dune shades or cooler evenings, and firing things up on freezing nights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/5584b3ed5f6dfb4ad28b012b781ad044.poster.avif?t=1756124621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/5584b3ed5f6dfb4ad28b012b781ad044.webm?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782090/extras/5584b3ed5f6dfb4ad28b012b781ad044.mp4?t=1756124621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
